Pat Nye https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Nye 0 Patricia Dorothy Nye, OBE (11 February 1908 – 11 April 1994) was an English actress-manager. She had a six-decade career, known in her later years for playing formidable women. She was appointed Officer of the Order of the British Empire (OBE) in the 1946 King's Honours List for her service as a chief officer in the Women's Royal Naval Service during the Second World War.
